                    <h4 class="mb2moduleintabs-article-title">Our Strategy - Vision</h4><div class="mb2moduleintabs-article-introtext"><p>"To improve the competitive advantage of our members by maximising the collective purchasing power and expertise of our membership"<br /><br /> Our future vision is to be our members&rsquo; principle route to suppliers and manufacturers. </p>
<ul class="vision">
<li>Helping members maintain their independence through the strength of collective purchasing collaboration, delivering the best products at the best value for our members&rsquo; customers.</li>
<li>Collectively delivering attractive large scale volumes for manufacturers and offering our suppliers substantial national retail opportunities.</li>
<li>To develop and add value to our members&rsquo; businesses across a number of areas as directed by the Board.</li>
