<section class="our-plan">
	<div class="containerTop">
		<div class="cell-4 plan-block lft-plan">
			<div class="block">
		<h3>WHERE IT ALL BEGAN ...</h3>
		<p>The collaboration of Scottish farmers began in 1903 with the formation of Tarff Valley Limited.</p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			1903		</span></div>
		</div>
				<div class="block">
		<h3>UNITED FARMERS IS BORN ...</h3>
		<p><p>United Farmers is formed, a co-operative organisation operating on a not-for-profit basis, with the clear aim of maximising the purchasing power of its members and promoting inter-member co-operation</p></p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			1971		</span></div>
		</div>
				<div class="block">
		<h3>OWN BRAND ...</h3>
		<p><p>Our range of own branded products, researched and developed with key manufacturers, provide United Farmers&rsquo; members with quality products at the right price</p></p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			2016		</span></div>
		</div>
		</div>

<div class="cell-2 plan-title">
	<div class="main-color extraBold">Our <br><span>Plan</span></div>
</div>

<div class="cell-4 plan-block rit-plan">
    		<div class="block">
		<h3>THE FOUNDATIONS ARE LAID ...</h3>
		<p>In 1968 managers from several co-operatives came together to discuss common problems and recognised the potential benefits to be gained by creating a joint purchasing programme for farm inputs.</p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			1968		</span></div>
		</div>
				<div class="block">
		<h3>CREATION OF TASK FORCES ...</h3>
		<p>Member specialist teams were formed in specific product sectors to work together to consolidate business with selected suppliers</p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			2008		</span></div>
		</div>
				<div class="block">
		<h3>LAUNCH OF UF INTERACTIVE ... THE SEQUEL! ...</h3>
		<p><p>Our web based site &ldquo;UF Interactive&rdquo; assists our chosen suppliers to communicate collectively and individually with our members. 2017 sees a makeover to bring the site up to date.</p></p>
		<div class="plan-year"><span>
			2017		</span></div>
		</div>
